OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1783698492
OL,3,CHospital ward closed due to outbreak
OL,4,Cof 'very contagious' form of scabies
OL,6,FA Carmarthenshire hospital has
OL,7,Fannounced it is closing one of its
OL,8,Fwards due to an outbreak of a rare and
OL,9,F'very contagious' form of scabies.
OL,11,FCrusted scabies has been identified on
OL,12,Fthe Steffan Ward at Glangwili
OL,13,FHospital, which the health board has
OL,14,Fconfirmed will now be closed to
OL,15,Fadmissions and transfers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
