PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1783698492
OL,3,CHospital ward closed due to outbreak
OL,4,Cof 'very contagious' form of scabies
OL,6,FHywel Dda University Health Board said
OL,7,Fpatients and staff who have been
OL,8,Fidentified as contacts, regardless of
OL,9,Fif they have contracted it or not,
OL,10,Fhave been informed and offered
OL,11,Ftreatment.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the health board
OL,14,Fsaid: "Steffan Ward at Glangwili
OL,15,FHospital is currently closed to
OL,16,Fadmissions and transfers while we
OL,17,Fmanage a scabies outbreak on the ward,
OL,18,Fin line with established infection
OL,19,Fprevention and control procedures...
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1783698492
OL,3,CHospital ward closed due to outbreak
OL,4,Cof 'very contagious' form of scabies
OL,6,F"Support and advice has been made
OL,7,Favailable through our Infection
OL,8,FPrevention and Control team and we are
OL,9,Fworking closely with partners to
OL,10,Fmanage the situation. Additional
OL,11,Finfection prevention and control
OL,12,Fmeasures have been implemented on the
OL,13,Fward, including enhanced monitoring,
OL,14,Ftreatment of identified contacts and
OL,15,Fongoing support from specialist teams.
OL,17,F"There is currently an increased
OL,18,Fprevalence of scabies within the
OL,19,Fcommunity across the Hywel Dda area,
OL,20,Fwhich is a contributory factor in
OL,21,Fhospital outbreaks."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
