OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1783698492
OL,3,CHospital ward closed due to outbreak
OL,4,Cof 'very contagious' form of scabies
OL,6,FThe team will monitor the outbreak
OL,7,Fclosely and say the ward will reopen
OL,8,Fwhen it is deemed safe to do so.
OL,10,FAccording to the NHS 111 Wales
OL,11,Fwebsite, crusted scabies is "a rare
OL,12,Fand very contagious type of scabies"
OL,13,Fthat can occur in people with weakened
OL,14,Fimmune systems.
OL,16,FSymptoms include a crusted, flaky rash
OL,17,F- often on the elbows, knees, hands
OL,18,Fand feet.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
